          <h3 class="section-sub">About the College</h3>

          <p class="about-para-1">
            RMDEC aspires to be a premier institution offering quality technical education and research with application
            expertise in Engineering and Technology. Develop the students as outstanding professionals by creating an
            environment that would nurture creativity, academic excellence, professionalism, high standard of ethics,
            sense of responsibility and respect for individuals. Provides an efficient academic and research environment.
          </p>
