            participate in any event.</span></div>
        <div><img class="check" src="check.png" alt=""></img><span>No registration fees will be collected.</span></div>
        <div><img class="check" src="check.png" alt=""></img><span>Participation certificate will be provided to all
            participants.</span></div>
        <div><img class="check" src="check.png" alt=""></img><span>The winners will be rewarded with cash prize.</span>
        </div>
